episodes.title: How I Almost Joined a Cult 😳 | Reaction to Hood Horror’s “Rise & Fall of Nature Boy” (Part 1)
episodes.description:
This one hit home in a way most won’t understand.
Years ago, I used to follow Nature Boy and his group every day — watched their lives unfold like a movie that kept getting darker. I never joined, but I was close. Too close.

So when Hood Horror dropped “The Rise & Fall of Nature Boy,” I had to react.
This video isn’t just entertainment for me — it’s a reality check, a memory, and a message.
If you ever got caught up watching this cult’s journey too, this one’s for you.

Drop your thoughts in the comments — were you watching back then too? 👀
And hit that like button so more people can see the truth for what it was.

🎥 Subscribe for more reactions that actually mean something.
